  m_text: "Trip, the mischievious, playful droid has stolen your AirPods and is hiding
    somewhere in the house! Use the sound of the music playing to locate him before
    the timer rounds out!\n\n>>> Spot \u2192 Sprint \u2192 Catch\n>>> Catch the droid
    3 times in a row to win\n>>> Follow the music! It gets louder as you get closer\n>>>
    Search rooms and check behind objects\n>>> If Trip escapes, track the sound and
    keep chasing\n>>> Catch Trip before the timer runs out!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
